   The stock market showed a small gain today,
continuing the sluggish pattern of the past two sessions.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials rose .83 to 2,048.24 in
the first half hour.
   Gainers slightly outnumbered losers in the overall tally of New
York Stock Exchange-listed issues, with 468 up, 446 down and 578
unchanged.
   Volume on the Big Board came to 19.47 million shares as of 10
a.m. on Wall Street.
   The market has been in a holding pattern since the start of the
