index was up .35 at 297.10.
   On Tuesday the Dow Jones industrial average dropped 2.66 to
2,047.41.
   Advancing issues outnumbered declines by about 10 to 9 on the
NYSE. Big Board volume totaled 133.17 million shares, against
131.89 million million in the previous session.
